description.en: PlanetWatch decentralizes, incentivizes, and gamifies environmental monitoring. Currently, we build dense air quality sensor networks streaming real-time data to our platform. Validated data earn Planet token rewards and build a global immutable air quality ledger on the Algorand blockchain. Sensing is mining!
